  <summary date="2017-10-12T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Equal Access to Quality Education Act of 2017

This bill requires the Department of Education to award competitive matching grants to partnerships between high-need local educational agencies and institutions of higher education to establish or support: (1) teacher preparation programs, and (2) teacher induction and retention programs.</summary>
